    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "第一回！　わんにゃんツインズ、フェス会議～！\nわんわんにゃんにゃ～ん！",
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの、その効果音？　でも、まさか私達二人で\nフェスのトリを務めることになるなんて、感無量ですわ",
      "startTime": 14.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "これまでは月スト五人で出てたフェスだよね。二人で\n出られるのは嬉しいけど、その分、頑張らないと！",
      "startTime": 24.2463623202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。そのためにも、会場が大いに盛り上がるような\n新しい試みがほしいですわね。芽衣、考えてきまして？",
      "startTime": 33.7000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　そのための会議だもん。芽衣が考えて\nきたのは～、ファンのみんなと一緒にもぐもぐタイム！",
      "startTime": 43.9666676839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3754.5584996000016,
          "startTime": 43.4333343506
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "もぐもぐ……？　面白そうな響きですが\n具体的には一体、何をするんですの？",
      "startTime": 55.3333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ中にね～、芽衣とすずにゃんが手作りした\nドーナツとポテトチップスを配って、もぐもぐするの",
      "startTime": 62.2366666477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "面白い案ですけれど……衛生面がちょっと……\nでも、『新しい演出』というのは賛成ですわ",
      "startTime": 72.6333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "例えばダンスに合わせてステージが変わったり\n香りがするスモークを歌に合わせて出したり",
      "startTime": 81.4666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "わ～、それ絶対盛り上がるよ！　ナイスアイデア！\n……あ、でも規模が大きいから、今から間に合うかなぁ",
      "startTime": 91.9853783064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "むむむ……とはいえ、まだ会議は始まったばかり\n他のことも含めて、決めていきますわよ！",
      "startTime": 105.1666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、{user}さんに言われていた\nセットリストの希望はバッチリ完成しましたわね",
      "startTime": 114.1333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "MCの内容も考えたし、後は練習するだけ……\nって言いたいけど、結局新しい演出は決まらなかったね",
      "startTime": 123.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……うーーーーん……",
      "startTime": 129.5060542747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ！　こころちゃんと愛ちゃん！　前に二人で\nライブをすることになった時に、合宿したんだって",
      "startTime": 141.8666665396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "必要であれば、私達も合宿していいそうですわよ\nせっかくですし、そこで考えるのもいいですわね",
      "startTime": 150.4333343507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん！　集中して練習も出来るし、それがいいよ！\nでもどこで合宿しよっか？　すずにゃんの別荘とか？",
      "startTime": 159.1736993477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "合宿はいつもあそこですし、たまには気分を変えたい\nですわねぇ。またオカピが逃げるかもしれませんし……",
      "startTime": 168.4666707358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……芽衣の家なんてどうでしょう？\nまだお邪魔したことありませんでしたし",
      "startTime": 177.8666707358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ナイスアイデアだよ～。お母さんはすずにゃん推しだし\n……あ、でも今はダメかも。妹がね、受験で忙しくて",
      "startTime": 186.0614337291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "お母様が私を……！？　芽衣の妹さんにも\n会ってみたかったですが……仕方ないですわね",
      "startTime": 197.9333424888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、かわりに芽衣のおばあちゃんちはどうかな？\n最近は行けてないけど、前はよく遊びに行ってたの",
      "startTime": 206.9085216739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "あら、きっとおばあ様も芽衣に会いたがっていますわね\nもし良ければ、私も行ってみたいですわ！",
      "startTime": 216.5666758222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、じゃあお願いしてみる。きっと芽衣の\nお友達も会いたがってると思うし。喜ぶだろうな～",
      "startTime": 224.0534587867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "むっ……こほん。芽衣、あくまで合宿なんですのよ？\nお友達に会いに行く時間なんてありませんわ",
      "startTime": 237.4000100456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
